posting_body: ['Newly Renovated Downstairs corner apartment with Huge Patio', 'Property Address', '11329 Otsego St. | 4 | North Hollywood, CA 91601', 'Offered By', '11329 Otsego St., LLC |', 'show contact info', 'Description', '11329 Otsego street North Hollywood, CA 91601', 'major cross street Tujunga and Magnolia- Connect to major 170 FWY & 101 FWY easy access to 405 FWY and 134 FWY', 'Amazing 2 Bedroom 2 Bathroom apartment in NOHO Arts District, directly across the street of Valley Village Park, with great jogging paths and exercise equipment.', 'Small 8-unit apartment complex with parking and laundry facility on-site.', 'Your new home has and open space concept with laminate wood like flooring throughout, modern light fixtures, and a huge enclosed patio.', 'The kitchen has gorgeous ceramic tiles and quartz counter tops, new cabinets, and stainless-steel sink and hardware.', 'Stainless steel fridge, microwave, stove and dishwasher included!', 'Lease terms:', 'We offer one year lease agreement, deposit is equivalent to one month’s rent , pet friendly with small pet deposit and breed restrictions.', 'Amenities', 'Laundry', 'Parking', 'Intercom', 'Secured Entry', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 2BD/2.0BA', 'Square Feet: 1,050', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $2,595.00', 'Available: 08/10/2022', 'Application Fee: $35.00', 'Security Deposit: $2,595.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Small dogs allowed']
